description: Kickstart your academic journey with Frosh, a spirited introduction to university life. Engage in team-building activities, connect with fellow students, and set the tone for an exciting year ahead.
WoW is a week-long celebration marking the commencement of the academic year. Dive into an array of engaging activities, workshops, and social events to welcome new and returning students.
Elevate your social experience with our Formal and Semi-Formal events. Dress in style and enjoy an evening of elegance, entertainment, and camaraderie.
Embrace the spooky season with Horrorland, a Halloween-themed event featuring thrilling activities, costume contests, and a chilling atmosphere
Forge valuable connections with professionals and peers through our Networking Events. Gain insights into various scientific fields and explore potential career paths.
